%N A395093 Number of transitive relations on an n-set with at most seven ordered pairs.
%H A395093 <a href="/index/Rec#order_15">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (15,-105,455,-1365,3003,-5005,6435,-6435,5005,-3003,1365,-455,105,-15,1).
%F A395093 a(n) = C(n,0) + C(n,1) + 10*C(n,2) + 136*C(n,3) + 2565*C(n,4) + 36981*C(n,5) + 350035*C(n,6) + 2200507*C(n,7) + 9502656*C(n,8) + 28893816*C(n,9) + 62455680*C(n,10) + 94857840*C(n,11) + 97130880*C(n,12) + 60540480*C(n,13) + 17297280*C(n,14).
%F A395093 a(n) = A394769(n) + A392460(n).
%e A395093 a(2) = 13, the same as the total number of transitive relations on a 2-set because every transitive relation on a 2-set has at most 7 (actually at most 4) ordered pairs.
%e A395093 a(3) = 170: of the 171 transitive relations on a 3-set, the only one excluded is the complete relation {1,2,3} x {1,2,3} with 9 > 7 ordered pairs.
